data.description: 1 bed 1 bathroom third floor unit in highly sought after FRONT STREET LOFTS of Lemont. Corner/end unit with expansive windows giving tons of natural light and scenic views. Freshly painted throughout with high end new vinyl flooring. Fabulous kitchen with upgraded cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, expansive island with seating and granite counter tops. Large bedroom with custom flooring. Bathroom with new tub surround, glass door and shower head. Exposed duct work, high ceilings and concrete add to the cool urban vibe of this space. Full size washer and dryer in unit.  Only 1 bedroom unit with an ncredible, private, outdoor covered terrace space with second balcony. Convenient downtown Lemont location near shopping, dining, Metra, expressway access, parks, walking trails,schools and The Forge Outdoor Adventure Park. Elevator building and garage parking included! Schedule your appointment today!
